HTML:a Markup Language for describing web documents ( یک زبان نشانه گذاری برای تضیح صفحات وب )

- a simple html code has this tags:
  <!DOCTYPE html>
  <html>
   <head>
  <title> hello world </title>    // TITLE OF THE WEB PAGE
  </head>
  <body>                          // INSIDE THE WEB PAGE
  my name is arash
  <p> my name is arash </p>       // paragraph tag
  <h1> اسم من</h1>               // heading tag (IT CAN BE DEVIDED IN 6 LEVEL: h1 to h6 becoming little
  
  </body> 
  </html>
  
CSS: is a stylesheet language that describes the presentation of a html document. (CSS = Cascading Style Sheet)
